            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_18gc' title='Col. 18GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 March 2003 vol 646 c18GC' name='column_18gc' href='#column_18gc' rel='bookmark'>18GC</a>
            the judiciary. They are fairly skilled people and would understand that what we are talking about is not any other Act but any other Act affected by the section.
          </p>
